{"tid":1813643,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【中国肺炎陰謀論】中共又想重施故技，將香港推向絕路，再扮好心拯救香港","createTime":"2020-01-06T12:07:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-06T12:10:01.000Z","uid":293677,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"1f5d32a3e08f0c3c77fde463fc3eb4d498a576a0","tid":1813643,"uid":293677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T12:07:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jWhwCfX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjWhwCfX.jpg&h=5add213b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">同2003年一樣，製造一場重大危機-<span style=\"color: red;\">沙士</span>，令香港重創。<br />\n然後中共出黎扮好人，推出益香港人既政策，想令香港人歸順。<br />\n開頭用經濟手段，慢慢令人麻目，之後就各個層面不斷滲透同洗牌。<br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n今次反送中運動，令香港人全面覺醒反共<br />\n中共想翻本，就係用呢招，<span style=\"color: red;\">製造一場同沙士同級既危機俾香港</span>-<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">中国肺炎</span></span><br />\n之後唔洗講都知。<br />\n<br />\n可能有人會問，點解先喺武漢爆發，而唔係香港??<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />純粹操作失誤，TK有咩出奇。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">以上言論，只係純屬幻想虛構創作鳩嗡吹水，切勿當真</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87f9f8b42d05d4c4f57959ad4fddca1b68049b39","tid":1813643,"uid":293677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T12:09:14.000Z","msg":"推一推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88706561499f4b3fbbbe78d38a9be87da738dd58","tid":1813643,"uid":331421,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T12:09:32.000Z","msg":"共產黨賤招"},{"pid":"09e5a3a3fa29310d53e86d63b3ed813001a45293","tid":1813643,"uid":293677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T12:10:01.000Z","msg":"大家有咩意見，隨便發表<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}